.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/10/20191004/20191004_165841_034.html</a><br />\n<br />\n睇新聞啦風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee9346ca25838ebaf65eb565b58fedce900d48a","tid":1746782,"uid":326897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1209b08e53111a5b4be6a1418c63ada3056033d5","tid":1746782,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"若果中午暫停投票，政府話會封存票箱下星期再投過。中間成個星期啲票有冇俾人攪根本冇人知。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪夜晚7，8投最穩陣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"你咁講幾點投都一撚樣，<br />\n佢要做手腳，你投唔投都做到，<br />\n緊係一早投撚咗佢啦，<br />\n我都係嗰句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要保皇仆街</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f9746bcafb219cae4938a9bca49d9b398e2be0d9","tid":1746782,"uid":232927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"我都覺得現在就話由投票後一直有人睇住，太少時間做手腳<br />\n如果佢封存票箱到下星期，會唔會做野就好難講，太長時間成個箱唔見都得<br />\n這幾日的風向好大規模叫人一朝早投，情況有點似當日叫人入去守大學，希望只係多疑"},{"pid":"696fcd629a12ea1748e35b5ec20622d6758b8e62","tid":1746782,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f06fee3fe8471db9b2c802ff082f0f613d8b58","tid":1746782,"uid":302944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"若果<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夜晚</span></span>暫停投票，政府話會封存票箱下星期再投過。中間成個星期啲票有冇俾人攪根本冇人知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉投票日當天，若某投票站因突發事件無法運作，而投票可於1.5小時內恢復，該投票站的開放時間會於同一日作相應延長。若投票站未能於1.5小時內恢復運作，該投票站的投票會押後至後備投票日，即12月1日（星期日）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果臨收票站先俾人攪。可以1&middot;5小時內恢復而投票站會延長運作。 恢復後因為剩下時間好短所以再俾人攪而要押後一星期的風險較細。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b73da06486abff04c26d797bbccb06241fd86f8c","tid":1746782,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9746bcafb219cae4938a9bca49d9b398e2be0d9","tid":1746782,"uid":232927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"我都覺得現在就話由投票後一直有人睇住，太少時間做手腳<br />\n如果佢封存票箱到下星期，會唔會做野就好難講，太長時間成個箱唔見都得<br />\n這幾日的風向好大規模叫人一朝早投，情況有點似當日叫人入去守大學，希望只係多疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"就係太多風向撚令我好擔心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">港共劇本：<br />\n<br />\n中午搵人攪》恢復唔到〉押後投票》封存票箱〉對已經封存嘅票大造手腳》建制大勝</span>"},{"pid":"ae762b9e5ea089c46a88d273020e05606848a18b","tid":1746782,"uid":293648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝美國總統, 唔係佢, 香港已經被解放軍殺死幾萬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dd7fcea09ea8b32c8736134fe7b7e09cfe6367e3","tid":1746782,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁撚樣都有得捉鬼?你係咪on9架? 拉</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1c8d9c64bd517c42ac3f348e7053375f73ca145","tid":1746782,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">on9<br />\n拉</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b36078c54ee7cead0e1ef0c025af3cbb88cd819c","tid":1746782,"uid":275020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1209b08e53111a5b4be6a1418c63ada3056033d5","tid":1746782,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"若果中午暫停投票，政府話會封存票箱下星期再投過。中間成個星期啲票有冇俾人攪根本冇人知。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪夜晚7，8投最穩陣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:51:41.000Z","msg"